ORIGINAL CONCEPT STATEMENT

The concept, architecture, and implementation of ai_code_her — specifically:

  - A unified multi-provider AI coding assistant environment for Android
  - Lightweight Termux-based client connecting to multiple AI APIs simultaneously
  - A single "ai" command switcher to toggle between AI providers seamlessly
  - Shared project workspace and unified HTTP server bridge for all AI providers
  - Zero local model requirement — API-only architecture on mobile

is an original invention by swordenkisk, conceived and developed in March 2026.

